Spell...........Casts...Interrupts..Fizzles Mob Resists        <br>
Rain of Fire....14......4...........1.......7                <br>
Rain of Lava....228.....7...........7.......210<br>
Rain of Spikes..212.....22..........4.......147                <br>
Rain of Swords..185.....9...........6.......129                <br>
<br>
<br>
since almost all of the casts were on single targets with resists adjusted by malise (or whatever) the resist rate is # resists  / ((# casts - # fizzles - # interrupts) *3)<br>
<br>
giving these rates<br>
Rain of Fire    25.9%<br>
Rain of Lava    32.7%<br>
Rain of Spikes  26.3% <br>
Rain of Swords  25.3%<br>
<br>
